  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Imovement
    public class Shark
extends Jumper
    A class of sharks as a special kind of jumpers. Appart from being able to jump they can also float on water. Sharks like to eat plants, but only alive plants. Sharks are immune for normal geological features.
    Author:
    Wannes Vande Cauter, Nils Van Dessel -- Fysica
